 |----------------------------------------------------------|
 |   insert mode window                                     |
 ------------------------------------------------------------

- Command mode -

 current available command are :
  - "i" : go to insert mode
  - "n" : perform a next in the play queue
  - "p" : perform a previous in the play queue
  - " " : perform a pause on the listening song
  - "m" : perform a mute
  - "q" : quit wur

- Insert mode -

 current available command are :
  - login
  - logout
  
 to implement :
  - play
  - stop
  - pause
  - next
  - prev
  - mute
  - wait
  - add
  - load
  - run
  - playlist
  - run
  - timetable
  - alias
  - add
  - delete




